thread.title: Daniel & Mariya
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Daniel & Mariya

author: Daniel & Mariya
title: Daniel & Mariya
text: Nuno has a fantastic ability to build relationships with his vendors. He was always quick to respond to questions or to provide feedback, no matter how many questions we may have asked along the journey - which also extended to him assisting us with our new property search. We were very happy with our sale result and with his excellent performance as our auctioneer on the day of our auction, we cant thank him enough!
